   <text type="letter">
      <body>
         
            <opener> 
               <salute>Dear father</salute>
            </opener>
         <p><choice><sic>i</sic><corr>I</corr></choice> now take the <choice><sic>plesure</sic><corr>pleasure</corr></choice> of writing a few lines <choice><sic>yo</sic><corr>you</corr></choice> hoping they find <choice><sic>yo</sic><corr>you</corr></choice> well <choice><sic>i</sic><corr>I</corr></choice> am quite well and in the <choice><sic>convalesent</sic><corr>convalescent</corr></choice> Camp i long to see yo and have a talk with yo <choice><sic>thair</sic><corr></corr></choice> <choice><sic>hante</sic><corr>haven't</corr></choice> <choice><sic>inny</sic><corr>any</corr></choice> news here we had a good dinner here to day</p>
         <p><choice><sic>father</sic><corr>Father</corr></choice> <choice><sic>yo</sic><corr>you</corr></choice> must excuse me for not writing a long letter for my hand <choice><sic>trembls</sic><corr>trembles</corr></choice> so that <choice><sic>i</sic><corr>I</corr></choice> <choice><sic>cant</sic><corr>can't</corr></choice> write well father write to me and if <choice><sic>yo</sic><corr>you</corr></choice> can come and see me good by for this time from Wm E Vandemark to friend Walt Whitman</p>
            <p><choice><sic>i</sic><corr>I</corr></choice> am in <choice><sic>barick</sic><corr>barrack</corr></choice> 43 <choice><sic>Addres</sic><corr>Address</corr></choice> Camp <choice><sic>Convalesint</sic><corr>Convalescent</corr></choice> <choice><sic>Elickazandry</sic><corr>Alexandria</corr></choice> [Soldiers nicknamed Alexandria "Camp Misery".]</p>
         
      </body>
